    "Adjust infectivity (default 0.3 = 30% transmission rate) for different diseases",
    "Change recovery_time (default 14 days) for disease duration",
    "Update initial populations for different outbreak sizes",
    "Calculate reproduction_number to assess epidemic potential"
  ],
